723640f-b.title: Manhattan: Union Square (West) - 16th Street - Broadway - [Union Square Park.]
723640f-b.text:
Union Square West, north from but not including 16th Street (east), to and including Broadway. Also seen is Broadway, east side, north from but not including 17th Street (east). A section of Union
Square Park is seen in the foreground.
May, 1924.
P. L. Sperr.
The same, from a different angle.
June, 1924.
P. L. Sperr.
